profile: At Master spas of Toronto, we have helped thousands of families escape their hectic lives. Whether by designing your perfect backyard outdoor oasis or your ultimate games room, let our knowledgeable staff provide solutions that will comfort and pamper you. We choose to offer our customers an unparalleled selection and value from a host of top brands which can be readily seen by visiting any of our Ontario warehouse showroom locations in Kitchener, Waterloo, Mississauga, Toronto or Barrie. With over 35 different spa models on display you will never have to buy from a picture. Buying wholesale direct gives our customers the best value and you can always rest assured that your purchase will be backed by the expertise and support of our service staff.
brands: Top hot tub and swim spa brands include award winning Master Spas, Twilight Series Spas and H2X Swim Spas.
payment_method: Payment methods that we can accept include Certified Bank Drafts, MasterCard, Visa, Amex and Cash

profile:
In our modern, hectic world, today's homeowners do not have the time or energy for the daily upkeep associated with most swimming pools. Durham Fiberglass Pools understands this and is proud to offer you high quality San Juan Fiberglass Pools, spas, and accessories. We provide a nearly maintenance-free centerpiece to the backyard resort you've always dreamed of, giving you more time with family and friends. With a state of the art fiberglass swimming pool you have the advantages of the lowest maintenance and upkeep of any pool in the industry, reduced operating costs, and the peace of mind that comes from having the best warranty in the industry.

Based in Durham Region, we service all of Southern Ontario including Toronto. We provide high-quality installation with the personal service that only a family-run business can offer.

At Durham Fiberglass Pools, we care about our customers.
